data.description: Immaculately maintained and Move In Ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on a large 1/3 acre lot in The Meadows Subdivision in Gillis. This charming traditional home is loaded with a terrific array of amenities to make it perfect for a family that likes to entertain.The open concept layout with an oversized chef's kitchen and rear porch is perfect for formal and informal gatherings. Large great room open to the kitchen which features custom stained cabinetry, island bar, and granite countertops. The master suite is sure to please with a jetted soaking tub, separate shower, and large walk-in closet. All bedrooms are spacious with ample closet space. The laundry room has extra storage for your cleaning needs. The home also has a wooden privacy fence that is only one year old.
